{"tid":884556,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慘！義大利港口暗夜冒火 數百輛瑪莎拉蒂燒光光","createTime":"2018-10-31T16:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T18:42:19.000Z","uid":56533,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2bc3854d1c29098ddb38c79cdacc6e20e6ea53","tid":884556,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l22Jxid0it8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl22Jxid0it8&d=iKnCVhzc%2BzzjKiEVI3UiRmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=cb76a129\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l22Jxid0it8</a><br />\n<br />\n遭受暴風雨侵襲的義大利，不但威尼斯3/4泡在水裡，薩沃納港（Savona）也冒出熊熊烈火，一把將數百輛各價值10幾萬美元的瑪莎拉蒂（Maserati）轎車燒光光！<br />\n<br />\n根據熱那亞港口管理部門消息，暴雨來襲，薩沃納港卻意外發生火災，原來是風雨挾帶海水入侵，停泊在港口正等著出口到中東地區的數百輛瑪莎拉蒂，因為海水鹽分引爆汽車電池造成爆炸，在當地時間30日凌晨3時30分左右發生火災，瞬間大火熊熊，數百輛汽車全部被燒毀。<br />\n<br />\n當地消防單位出動10多名消防人員全力搶救，卻無濟於事，2個停車場遭到海水淹過，每輛價值至少10幾萬美元的瑪莎拉蒂，全部燒到只剩骨架。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/161/5bd8fff5602b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F161%2F5bd8fff5602b5.jpg&h=3e5d527e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外電報導，這是薩沃納港1星期以來的第2場火災，而27日起，義大利就被暴雨等惡劣天氣狂打，國內交通幾乎癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n瑪莎拉蒂是義大利賽車與跑車生產商製造，過去曾是法拉利跑車的一部分，現在屬於飛雅特克萊斯勒汽車，每輛售價至少12萬美元。2018台北國際新車大展，2018年式的小改款GranTurismo Sport報價758萬元台幣（約24萬美元）起，而2018年式小改款GranTurismo車系的頂級性能車型：GranTurismo MC，甚至開出838萬元台幣（約26.8萬美元）的建議售價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-10-31/160079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2018-10-31%2F160079&d=iKnCVhzc%2BzzjKiEVI3UiRmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=bfdf2263\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-10-31/160079</a>"},{"pid":"e518db1ca07eb3761ee6ecb75c972d5d79bc39f9","tid":884556,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d89b8b3e6b71db4809cb8a0a3d51ab9d824b90f","tid":884556,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"中國富豪撻訂，一把火燒哂d車，再claim 燕梳"},{"pid":"3c7b175c234f6d1c6e777e1c0bdfc62d196196eb","tid":884556,"uid":18955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9d89b8b3e6b71db4809cb8a0a3d51ab9d824b90f","tid":884556,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"中國富豪撻訂，一把火燒哂d車，再claim 燕梳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:39:36.000Z","msg":"心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05873468d4989deedc78c4c817f390a2e136c4e","tid":884556,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:42:19.000Z","msg":"10多名消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}